2011-07-08T09:25:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/universal-inc-june-sales-fall-21-34-table-1325-tt.html
UNIVERSAL INC (1325)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 21.34% to NT$78,674,000 from NT$100,022,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             78,674          100,022    
YOY%             -21.34%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            573,173          542,750    
YOY%              5.61%  
=================================================================
 